org.apache.paimon.operation

Class LocalOrphanFilesClean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.operation.OrphanFilesClean
      • org.apache.paimon.operation.LocalOrphanFilesClean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class LocalOrphanFilesClean
extends OrphanFilesClean
    Local OrphanFilesClean, it will use thread pool to execute deletion.

    Note that, this class will be used when the orphan clean mode is local, else orphan clean will use distributed one. See `FlinkOrphanFilesClean` and `SparkOrphanFilesClean`.
